In statements during a breakfast of the Association of Directors and Executives of Arag<0xC3><0xB3>n (ADEA), Olavarrieta has stated that the concentration process is being undertaken "at the highest possible speed, and we have to be very satisfied with how it is occurring in the deadlines that in their day, not now, were marked in the business plans with the Bank of Spain", he emphasized.
